  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for clamav",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for clamav fixes the following issues:\n\nClamAV version 1.4.3:\n\n- CVE-2025-20260: PDF Scanning Buffer Overflow Vulnerability (bsc#1245054).\n- CVE-2025-20234: Vulnerability in Universal Disk Format (UDF) processing (bsc#1245055).\n\nOther bugfixes:\n\n- Fix a race condition between the mockup servers started by different test cases in freshclam_test.py (bsc#1243565)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
